---
title: Mediterranean Chickpea Salad Wraps with Spinach, Tomato, and Cucumber
description: Looking for an easy dinner you can whip up in 15 minutes without ever turning on your oven or stove? These chickpea salad wraps check all the boxes! The ever-adaptable ‘banzo bean is mashed with mayo, mustard, hummus, paprika, lemon, and shallot to form a luscious salad. Then it’s wrapped up tight in flour tortillas with spinach, cucumber, and tomatoes for freshness in every bite. Once you’re finished with dinner, you’ll be delighted to find you have approximately zero pans or baking sheets to wash! Now that’s a wrap.
